{"pageProps":{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji50","name":"毛泽东全集第50卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji50.pdf"],"article":{"title":"关于“农村包围城市”的口号","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于“农村包围城市”的口号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1967年7月）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在提出“农村包围城市”这个口号是反动的。过去革命条件下，提出这个口号是对的。但现年的情况变了，城市住的无产阶级，你用农村包围城市干什么？包围城市就是包围无产阶级，包围革命造反派。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":7}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":34,"page_end":34},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]},"__N_SSG":true}